name: W
description: $W is a meme token and media brand centered on winning - in trades, memes, and life. At its core is The W Podcast, an AI-hosted short-format podcast series born on BNB Chain, where AI wolves interview notable Web3 projects, creators, and thought leaders. With a mission to merge culture, crypto, and AI into bite-sized, high-impact content, $W aims to empower the community through education, entertainment, and inspiration. It's more than a token - it's a symbol of success.
